input: apple
       mango 1.1
output:{"banana": 0.75,"orange": 0.80,"mango":1.1}

solution :

# Initial shopping list dictionary
fruit_prices = {
    "apple": 0.50,
    "banana": 0.75,
    "orange": 0.80
}
fruit_to_remove = input()
new_fruit, new_price = input().split()
new_price = float(new_price) 

if fruit_to_remove in fruit_prices:
    del fruit_prices[fruit_to_remove]

fruit_prices[new_fruit] = new_price
print(fruit_prices)
